Ability to store gift cards/coupons/ time expiring discounts to stores.
secondary market for selling and purchasing gift cards.
If there was a site where customers picked out goods and generated a cart que.
we on the backend can see the cart contents and if people want to sell their gift cards we can automatically
use the card balances to purchase requested goods and credit the card seller minus the 10-25% of
the cards value which is the incentive to the user to use our service because they get discounts.
meanwhile card sellers get instant anonymous settlement for their gift card's monetary value.
